	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>FHorse</b> [ Sat Aug 04, 2012 8:13 am ]</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Version 0.64</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Changelog:<br />0.64<br />Rewrite from scratch the audio subsytem and now there are two new options in the &quot;Audio&quot; menu, &quot;Low&quot; and &quot;High&quot; quality.<br />&quot;Low&quot; is the old engine, &quot;High&quot; is the new engine. Just try to hear the difference.<br />Fixed many bugs in APU emulation which is now much more accurate.<br />Added the ability to have a portable version of the emulator. Just rename the executable:<br />Linux:<br />punes32 -&gt; punes32_p<br />punes64 -&gt; punes64_p<br />Windows<br />punes32.exe -&gt; punes32_p.exe<br />punes64.exe -&gt; punes64_p.exe<br />When the executable becomes a portable version, it create and use the folder where is the exe as the root folder.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


